texts.text: Patch 42 was a version of Wii U Edition released on December 18, 2018.[1] [edit]
Added The Nightmare before Christmas mash-up pack.

Fix for crash that would occur while near snowy biomes.
Fixed barrier block in the tutorial level.
Fix for crash that would occur when TNT blows up a fence post and a shulker box.
